{
  "stem": "11499.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I give you some vodka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Come on!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was raining.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no border guards, because it was raining.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we came up about four miles from Berlin at the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the train was going very, very slow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the train hit us, hit our truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they had to fix the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the three of you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Freddy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and two Russians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they fixed the truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took a whole day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came to Berlin in the Eastern Zone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll never forget, down on Rigaer Strasse was a Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we registered there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we registered-- Elly comes from the English Zone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Elly-- yeah, Elly was pregnant then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we registered, because we want to go to her town, Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we-- we went to the-- the Americans took us from the Eastern Zone, in a big truck, to the American Zone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we took the train to Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the city gave us where to stay, with somebody, some German couple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from there, we went to Frankfurt am Main.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We went to DP camp Zeilsheim, near Frankfurt am Main.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- I worked for the American Army Signal Service Corps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We used to divide food for the American Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From there, I-- we decided we want to go to-- to Israel, to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to a kibbutz to learn how to work on the land, to be a farmer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We stayed there for-- Where was that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Fulda, near Fulda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near Fulda, where my daughter was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
